Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:01.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:03.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:05.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:11.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:13.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:17.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mysterious robberies in the middle\nof the night...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:20.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The culprit enters leaving no clues\nand is never seen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:24.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be the work of a demon\nwho can really become invisible?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:04.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku is on the verge of\ncompleting the Sacred Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:09.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Learning that, we continue our journey\nin search of the few remaining shards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And who'd have thought that\nduring our travels,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}we'd come upon that\nold woman again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:18.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons, away with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:24.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A bit miserable for a dinner, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:27.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't be helped! We didn't\ncatch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all out of your\nninja food, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:31.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:34.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, why didn't you stock\nup on more food?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I would have, if my pockets\nhad been full of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're out of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:43.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. So we'll have to earn some\nmoney along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:46.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:47.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ehh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:52.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just about done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:54.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:05.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm bigger, so I'm hungrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a growing boy,\nso I need more food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Hah!\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:16.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if you can win against me!\NNot a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:17.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:18.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:23.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Now!\N- No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll be able to eat our fill\ntomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stupid Inuyasha!\NJust you wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:48.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll get back at you\nfor taking what's mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Madam Exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:03.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:07.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This wind seems ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just the wind picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It struck again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Madam Exorcist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:24.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Madam Exorcist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've been robbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:27.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He struck a different house\nthis night!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is quite a lively town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know if we'll be able\nto find any house
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in need of sutra charms\nor exorcisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Makes no difference since\nyour exorcisms are fake anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:52.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even then, unless the house\nhas some kind of problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it will not go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:56.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will not go smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He shouldn't be proud\nof what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:01.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At this rate, even if we're\nin a town like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we won't be able to\nsleep in an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong with sleeping outdoors?\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:07.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to take a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I want to sleep on\na nice, warm bedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I want to eat\ngood food, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll second that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:17.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So whaddya suggest?\NThere ain't nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, you {\i1}all....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been a while.\NHow have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the {\i1}old....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:23.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Exorcist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:28.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm... A demonic aura?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't sense anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:34.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some exorcist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:38.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:42.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Come get me!{\i0}\N- {\i1}Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demon, disperse!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:45.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:46.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:47.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:51.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop it, you two!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You still have much to learn\nabout life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! You fake exorcist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure about her\nskills as an exorcist,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she's pretty sharp\nwhen it comes to women.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were worried, weren't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:09.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That the monk and the princess\nwere getting along too well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:10.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:14.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You like him, don't you?\NThat monk, Miroku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ohh... it's written all over\nyour face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said, it's not like that!\NHuh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing?\NI'll leave you behind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You seem to be doing very well,\NMadam Exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:36.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that's why I can still\npursue my work as an exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's still doing exorcisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm amazed at how she\nmanages to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:44.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm glad that you've\ncome to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you help me with\na certain job?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd like no one better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:50.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there some profit to\nbe made here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:53.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, I just can't\nhandle this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:56.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I was just looking\nfor some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then,\nlet us hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mysterious happenings in\nthe dead of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only the homes of\nthe wealthy are targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how tight the security,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:12.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,something manages to break into\nthe house and steal everything of value.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And since the methods used\nare too mysterious for the usual thief,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,rumor has it that a demon\nis responsible for these evil deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean by\nmysterious methods?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:25.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The house can be tightly locked,\nbut the thief still enters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And even if someone senses\nan ominous presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,nothing is ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:30.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words, it's said that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this thief can go through walls\nand become invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:36.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's impossible, even\nfor a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then does it mean it really\ncan become invisible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An invisible demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:45.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it's not the work of humans,\nthen it must be a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The enemy is undoubtedly\nusing demon magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll see through his tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:56.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe you can see his tricks,\nbut I'll sniff him out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:59.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're always being duped by\ndemon magic, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the only magic you perform\nis to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:03.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I let myself get tricked\non purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:09.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kah!\N- Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:15.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?\NLet us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the town's second\nrichest household.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:24.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:29.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Both the richest and second richest\nhomes have been robbed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:31.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I've been employed\nby both.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:34.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I want to break up into two groups\nand stake out each house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Two groups? How do you want\nto divide up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't team up with Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn right! We don't need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha will end up being\ntricked by demon magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll cut down the robber\nwith my Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well first, Miroku and I must\nwork separately
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,since we both use\nspiritual powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:56.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Spiritual powers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, can you watch over\nthe old woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:05.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you, the other girl,\ngo with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I'm on Miroku's team?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku will probably be more\neffective than that old woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku's more useful\nthan that old hag.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Inuyasha goes\non that side,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,no one will be there\nto control him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My thoughts exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:25.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you help the exorcist\nwith your fox-demon magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? With my demon magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:32.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can run to us if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:37.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I'll use my fox-demon magic to\nuncover the robber's true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, I leave you in charge\nof this house, Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're off to the town's\nrichest house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please do your best\nto help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:54.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon or whatever,\nthis thing only strikes at night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All we can do is wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:59.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, let us rest and save\nour strength for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You think it's all right\nto ask for a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you tell them it's in\npreparation for tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:06.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure they won't object.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:10.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So let's just relax and\nenjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:15.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if Shippo and the others\nare all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:18.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He seems so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:25.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, his house may be\nbroken into tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:27.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what are we going to do\nfrom now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:29.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was going to come\nup with a {\i1}plan....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? The tea leaf is\nstanding up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is a good omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What kind of plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:37.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You really know how to\nuse demon magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And can you disappear, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:45.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't, but I've heard of\ndemon magic like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:48.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never heard of\ndemons who can become invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:49.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Neither have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:52.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although I have a talisman that\ncan hide your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a trick like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the enemy can hide,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then we shall do the same\nand hide ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:02.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we try combining them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right! It's worth a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:10.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:11.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hidden Cloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:15.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:21.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All {\i1}right....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:25.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It works!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:29.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How was it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:30.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! I now possess\na new power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's try it on other things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox Magic!\NHidden Cloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've perfected the technique\nof Hidden Cloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:51.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? {\i1}Right....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:58.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I need to do something\nbefore we slay the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be back by sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? He left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0} I must go out\nfor just a while, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:14.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:24.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! If you want it back,\nturn around three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boys, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:31.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:33.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A talking cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....{\i0} A demon cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:49.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:00.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh stop it, Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:07.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, no. I'm dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then say {\i1}it....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:18.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you bear my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ohh....{\i0} My goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:23.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yikes! She saw me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you call out to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:30.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....{\i0} Well....your {\i1}hips....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:31.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:31.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:32.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:36.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-oh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:44.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:48.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}By this time,\nshe'd have intervened...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? Why is she so silent?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does she follow\nme without a word?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:55.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And... What is that sutra\non her forehead?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it some kind of\nmessage for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monk....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How come you're so\nsilent all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:07.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'm speechless because\NI'm surrounded by such pretty women.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:08.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:13.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry! Hurry and lash out at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is she acting so differently?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:17.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk, sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The food here is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:28.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,P-Please go easy on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:29.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're going to censure me,\nsay it loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what is that sutra\non your forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it directed at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:41.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:45.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:49.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See you?\NWhat do you mean, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:50.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}no....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wasn't that Shippo just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's with this kid?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:01.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo! You think you're\nbeing funny or something!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:05.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:09.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn that Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know what he's up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:14.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but that kid kicked me several\ntimes and ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:16.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's how close you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:17.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:21.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You and Shippo fight so much\nbecause you're close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:25.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Shippo is much smaller,\nso go easy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:27.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like I care! Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha has a keen\nsense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He must have caught\nmy scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:40.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's hope that the invisible\ndemon doesn't have a sharp nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err.... Shippo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:43.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0} It's {\i1}nothing....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:47.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It will be dark soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've been asked to guard this\nfamily's {\i1}heirloom....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a precious scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:52.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The invisible demon has been\nstealing scrolls and rolls of silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then....We've had our {\i1}dinner....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:07.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And taken a {\i1}bath....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All that's left is to wait\nfor the culprit to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if he'll show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What if he doesn't show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:14.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:16.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean we have to stay\non guard without rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:20.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you can go sleep\nin the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:22.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll stay up as long as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It may not be this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, I wonder which\nhouse will be hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you sense something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh right... that's how she is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:38.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He made himself hidden\nback in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:42.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if that demon were\nto enter the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo can't be seen,\nso he'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:50.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:38.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! The hanging scrolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:13.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:24.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what do you think\nyou guys are doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:27.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:30.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}bad....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango! Old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:58.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How'd this guy get inside\nthe house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:19:59.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he's not invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it to {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me the {\i1}treasures....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:16.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:18.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He is an invisible demon, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He hasn't disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:20.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You demon! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn demon! Where are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Give me the treasures!\N- Here?! Or here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why're you stumbling around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks like you're guarding\nthe treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:41.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:43.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:58.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the only one with\nan unfamiliar scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Inuyasha!\N- Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:03.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:10.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you will turn over everything\nyou've stolen until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:20.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Things which are thin and shiny\nattract me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I couldn't help\nbut take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:23.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So many of {\i1}them....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:24.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Should we divide them\nup amongst ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:26.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're giving them back\nto their rightful owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well, I'm sure we'll\nbe richly rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My new Fox Magic trick\nwas almost complete, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:34.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,New Fox Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:36.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I ended up being saved\nby you, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:37.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've still got lots to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:38.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:40.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you've learned your lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:42.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,don't come near human\nsettlements again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.\NI'm off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:48.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! He's paper-thin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:50.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why he looked\nas though he was invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:54.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I really thought the invisible\ndemon had appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:55.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I was terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:57.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you stupid, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:58.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:01.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An {\i1}invisible{\i0} demon wouldn't "appear"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:03.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:48.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Akitoki came to us with\na nagging family problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:52.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,According to his story, he had set out\non a journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:53.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to seal the demon halberd known\nas the Naginata of Kenkon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:56.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was the ancestor of Hojo, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:23:59.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And on the genealogy scroll which\nhad been passed down to his family,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.11,0:24:00.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw the name Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.91,0:24:03.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What if I couldn't return\nto the modern age
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:05.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and end up married to Akitoki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:09.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"An Ancestor Named Kagome"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:12.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense a storm brewing!
